paragraphs.text:
%psql

SELECT day, COUNT(appname) as Count
from application_hits
WHERE appname = 'kubernetes-master'
GROUP BY day
ORDER BY day;

%psql

SELECT day, COUNT(appname) as Count
from application_hits
WHERE appname = 'keystone'
GROUP BY day
ORDER BY day;

%psql

SELECT day, COUNT(appname) as Count
from application_hits
WHERE appname IN ('leostream-broker', 'openstackscaler')
GROUP BY day
ORDER BY day;
